  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b88\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b8f\u0ba9\u0bcd - \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Why the protesters were detained in Calicut - Army explanation",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Military spokesman Brigadier Nishantha Premaratne said the protesters at Calicut had been evacuated to avoid distracting the cricketers.",
        "He mentioned that we did not remove the demonstrators from there but stopped their demonstration and mentioned that the demonstrations were stopped because the attention of the cricketers would be affected.",
        "Demonstrators holding banners; Due to this the batsmen were distracted and an order was issued to remove them. This incident took place on Wednesday and yesterday.",
        "The Bar Association of Sri Lanka has expressed dissatisfaction with the forcible removal of protesters in Calicut.",
        "In a letter to the police chief and the army commander, the Bar Association of Sri Lanka pointed out that the police and army had evicted protesters in Calicut who were critical of the president and the government.",
        "The Bar Association of Sri Lanka has stated that there is no reason to remove the protestors due to the fact that the perimeter of Kalikota is a public area."
      ],
